OL,6,FA 79-year-old man who subjected a
OL,7,Fchild to years of "sickening abuse"
OL,8,Fhas been jailed.
OL,10,FBrian Michael Carr, from Danby near ,
OL,11,Fhad previously been found guilty of
OL,12,Fseven offences including rape,
OL,13,Finciting a child to engage in sexual
OL,14,Factivity and sexual assault.
OL,16,Fbegan investigating Carr after the
OL,17,Fvictim reported her ordeal in 2021.
OL,19,FCarr appeared at Crown Court was
OL,20,Fsentenced to 15 years and four months
OL,21,Fin prison.
