OL,6,F"Investigations like these rarely mean
OL,7,Fthat only the victim has suffered.
OL,8,FThere is often a wider impact on the
OL,9,Fvictim's family.
OL,11,F"Sadly, no conviction or sentence for
OL,12,Foffences of this terrible nature can
OL,13,Frepair the damage that has already
OL,14,Fdone.
OL,16,F"I just hope the victim can draw
OL,17,Fstrength from the outcome a court and
OL,18,Fstart to rebuild her life."
